If you fall into the category of warm skin undertones, choose lipsticks that are like that too. You can tell by the fact that they gravitate towards orange, coral, gold or brown shades.
You may find that some veins look green and others look blue. If that's the case, congratulate yourself - you don't have to look at the undertone and can just focus on your colour preferences.
